Based on https://docs.sui.io/build/install

1. Install rust - https://www.journaldev.com/39960/install-rust-on-ubuntu-linux
2. Install the other linus libraries as per https://docs.sui.io/build/install
3. Install the binary as per https://docs.sui.io/build/install:

   cargo install --locked --git https://github.com/MystenLabs/sui.git --branch "devnet" sui sui-gateway
   
4. Check your sui address:

   sui client active-address
   
5. Request tokens in the #devnet-faucet channel using the syntax: 

   !faucet <YOUR_ADDRESS>, for example:
